      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Chef</span>
        <h2>Twenty years of meals made with care.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Our head chef has served Azalea Estates residents for more than two decades &mdash; and the dining room shows it. Familiar comfort, seasonal variety, and every plate presented with genuine pride.</p>
        <p>We believe that great food is at the heart of a great day. Our culinary team plans menus around what residents actually love to eat, with classic Southern favorites taking center stage alongside lighter fare and seasonal specialties. Dietary needs and personal preferences are always accommodated &mdash; just ask.</p>
        <div class="signature">
          <div class="signature__avatar">{{ icon('utensils', 22) }}</div>
          <div class="signature__text">
            <strong>3 meals daily, 7 days a week</strong>
            Restaurant-style service in our elegant dining room
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOUTHERN COOKING SECTION -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Southern at Heart</span>
      <h2>Food that feels like home.</h2>
      <p>Azalea Estates is known throughout Fayette County for its authentic Southern-style cooking &mdash; the kind of meals that bring residents to the table with something to look forward to.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="amenities-grid">
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('utensils', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Classic Southern Favorites</h4>
          <p>From biscuits and gravy at breakfast to slow-cooked suppers in the evening, our menus reflect the cuisine residents grew up with.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('leaf', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Seasonal &amp; Fresh</h4>
          <p>Menus rotate through the seasons, making the most of local produce and giving residents something new to enjoy throughout the year.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('heart', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Dietary Accommodations</h4>
          <p>Low-sodium, diabetic-friendly, texture-modified, and other dietary requirements are handled with the same care as every other plate we serve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('users', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Private Dining Rooms</h4>
          <p>Planning a birthday, holiday, or family gathering? Our private dining spaces are available for special occasions, with catering by our own kitchen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('shield', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Nutritional Balance</h4>
          <p>Each menu is planned with residents&rsquo; health in mind: increased mental acuity, sustained energy, and better management of chronic conditions all start at the table.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('clock', 22) }}</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Flexible Dining Hours</h4>
          <p>We know schedules differ. Our dining room operates with flexible seating times so residents can eat on their own rhythm without missing a meal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

