        <h2>A meal is more than food &mdash; it&rsquo;s connection.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Our elegant dining room is designed to feel like a welcoming restaurant, not a cafeteria. White linens, attentive service, and the warm conversation of neighbors who have become friends.</p>
        <p>Mealtimes are the social center of daily life at Azalea Estates. We invite residents to bring family for lunch, celebrate anniversaries over a private dinner, and simply enjoy each other&rsquo;s company at the table. No rushing, no noise &mdash; just the pleasure of a well-made meal shared with people who matter.</p>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>Breakfast, lunch &amp; dinner daily</li>
          <li>Restaurant-style table service</li>
          <li>Seasonal holiday menus</li>
          <li>In-room delivery when needed</li>
